\id 2TH
\h 2 THESSALONIANS
\toc1 Id ash d Hema Ep Paul Oꞌohana am ha Wui g Thessalonica t Am Wohochuddam
\toc2 2 THESSALONIANS
\toc3 2Th
\mt1 Id ash d Hema Ep Paul Oꞌohana am ha Wui g Thessalonica t Am Wohochuddam
\c 1
\m 
\v 1 T-wepnag mam am kih Thessalonica t am:
\p Am ant ep wo i em-oꞌohani ahni Paul. K ia ni-wehmaj g Silas ch Timothy k ch am i ni-wehmaj.
\p Dam woho hemajkamgaj g t-ohg Jiosh ab i e dagitok t-kownalig Jesus Christ wui.
\p 
\v 2 Ab o wa si s-em-hoꞌigeꞌid g t-ohg Jiosh g t-kownalig Jesus Christ wehm ch ab wo wa baꞌich i em-mahkad g i wehmtadag ch s-ap tahhadkam.
\s1 Matsh hekid wo i e ai g geꞌe lodaita
\p 
\v 3 Chum ach hekid ab si hoꞌigeꞌid g Jiosh em-hekaj, t-wepnag. Am amsh si i gewkahim e-wohochudadag ed ch baꞌich i si pihk e elid ab aꞌai e wui.
\v 4 Kuch heg hekaj si s-ap t-tahtk ch wehsko ha ahgidahim g t-wehm wohochuddam ab em-amjed. Msh am em-shoꞌigchud nam pi ab s-wohochud g Jiosh. Kumsh eda s-ap ab nakog g e-shoꞌigdag am wehhejed g Jiosh.
\v 5 Id o am wohokamchud mat am i em-apꞌech g Jiosh e wehhejed k pi ab hu haꞌichu wo em-abch am lodaita ch ed. Am am e shoꞌigchud wehhejed g Jiosh kownaltalig. K g Jiosh hab em-elid mam d s-apꞌekam ch am wo i em-wahpki e-kihdag ed.
\v 6 Jiosh at s-ap hab wo juh g lodaita. Hegam mo em-shoꞌigchud at wo e shoꞌigch heg hekaj.
\v 7 Kumt ahpim wo e doꞌibia ab amjed g e-shoꞌigchudadag. Jiosh at hab wo juh ihda mat hekid ep wo jiwia g t-kownalig Jesus ab dahm kahchim t amjed. T ia wehmaj wo dada g anghiligaj k wo si s-gewkdagk.
\v 8 T ia wehmaj ep wo e chehgi g si geꞌe mei. T wo s-koꞌokam ha namkid g Jesus hegam mo pi mahch g Jiosh ch pi ab hu wohog elid g s-kehg haꞌichu ahgaj ab amjed g t-kownalig Jesus.
\v 9 Hegam at gam hu wo si i e gawulkai ab amjed g Jiosh k pi hekid wo bei g geꞌe gewkdaj k chum hekid ab wo beihid g s-koꞌok e-namkidadag.
\v 10 Id at hab wo e juh mat hekid ia ep wo jiwia g t-kownalig Jesus. Kut g gewkdaj am haha wo i chehgi mat t-doꞌibia k ab i t-gawulkai e wehhejed.
\p 
\v 11 Pegih, heg ach hekaj chum hekid ab t-hoꞌigeꞌidahun Jiosh wui am em-wehhejed. Ab at i em-wai mamt wo e doꞌibia k d wo aꞌaligajk. M hab hahawa s-junimk g s-apꞌekam ab s-wohochudch. Kuch ab tahni g Jiosh mat am e-tatchui oidk hab wo em-juh k hab s-ap hab wo em-elidad. Jiosh o gewkdag mat hab wo juh ihda mach ab tahni.
\v 12 Kumt ab wo si haꞌichuchudad g t-kownalig Jesus. T heg hab waꞌap ab wo si em-haꞌichuchudad. Jiosh at si s-hemajim am i apꞌech g e-alidag wehm mat id hab wo em-juni.
\c 2
\s1 Matsh g Jiawul pionag ab wui wo kekiwua g Jiosh si Kehsha
\p 
\v 1 Bach wa em-ahgid mat ep wo jiwia g t-kownalig Jesus Christ k ab e wui wo i t-ui.
\v 2 Kush am hema em-ahgid mat heki hu hab e juh. Pi g am wo shaꞌi e kudut k pi shaꞌi ha wohochud, chum as hems hab wabsh e wua mo heg am ha tashogid g Jiosh o atp hems em-ahgid matt ahchim hab masma haꞌichu oꞌoha.
\v 3-4 Koi at e ai. Hemho wa at wehpeg am hab wo e juh mat muꞌi ab wui wo gegokiwua g Jiosh hegam mo hab chum kaij mo ab s-wohochud. T am hahawa hema wo i wuhsh g oꞌodham k wehs ha baꞌiwechkim d wo pi apꞌekamk ch d wo si obgajk g Jiosh ch am wo i wah geꞌe cheopi ch ed am Jerusalem t am k am wo dahiwua mat g hemajkam ab wo jiosht. Kut pi wo ha hiwigi mas haꞌichu ep wo jioshgak. T g Jiosh s-koꞌokam wo namkidad chum hekid.
\p 
\v 5 Am am wa s-chegito mani wa am wa heki hu em-ahgid ihda mani eda am em-wehmaj.
\v 6-7 S-mahch am mo g pi apꞌekam an e shohbidch hemu. T wabshaba has tash in hu hab wo i e juh hegai mo an shohbidch.
\v 8-11 T am haha wo i wuhsh hegai si pi apꞌekam oꞌodham. T g jijawul ha-geꞌejig Satan ab wo mah g gewkdag. Kut hab wo juh g nahnko mahs s-hasig haꞌichu ch s-ta neidamam haꞌichu mat wo ha iattogi g hemajkam. Kut hegam ab wo i s-wohoch mo hedai d pi e doꞌibiakam. Jiosh at hab wo ha juh mat wabsh g haꞌichu iattogi ab wo s-wohoch no pi idam s-hohhoꞌid g pi apꞌekam ch pi ab hu wo bei g wohokam mat hekaj wo chum e doꞌibia. T am haha wo jiwia g t-kownalig Jesus k si s-masma ab wo e chehgid k ab ab wo ihbhe hegai si pi ap oꞌodham k hekaj wo muꞌa k gam hu wo si i daꞌich mamt hebai wo ha nehnich g jijawul.
\v 12 T hegam mo e iattogid ch ab s-wohochud hab waꞌap ab wo bei g s-koꞌok e-namkidadag.
\s1 Mamt am i e gawulkai mamt wo e doꞌibia
\p 
\v 13-14 Mt wabshaba ahpim wo e doꞌibia ab amjed g s-koꞌok e-namkidadag. Si o pihk e elid g t-kownalig Jesus Christ em-hekaj. Kumt am wehmaj ab wo e haꞌichuchudad. Gd hu i si wehpeg at am i apꞌech g Jiosh mat g Hekia S-apꞌekam Gewkdag ab wo i em-gawulkai wehhejed. Kumt ab i s-wohoch ihda s-kehg haꞌichu ahgaj mach wa am em-ahgid. Id ach hekaj ab i hoꞌigeꞌid g Jiosh.
\v 15 Pegih, am ach wa em-mashcham ihda wohokam ch am ep em-oꞌohanid ab amjed. Kumt s-wihnam wo gegokkad ch an wo uꞌukchid.
\p 
\v 16 Ab o t-wui si pihk e elid g t-kownalig Jesus Christ g Jiosh t-ohg wehm ch ab si s-t-hoꞌigeꞌel. Kuch heg hekaj ab wui t-gewpkadch.
\v 17 Ahchim ach ab tahni mat ab wo i em-gewpkadch mamt g s-apꞌekam am hab wo junihid ch hab wo kaijjid.
\c 3
\s1 Mo g Paul ab i ha tahni g hoꞌigeꞌidahuna
\p 
\v 1 Ab g wo e hoꞌigeꞌidahun, t-wepnag, k ab wo tai g Jiosh mat pi ab hu wo e shohbi g haꞌichu t-ahga ab amjed t-kownalig Jesus. T muꞌijj ab wo si has i elid k ab wo s-wohog el hab masma mo am hab e wua em-shahgid.
\v 2 Pi ap hehemajkam o pi ab hu wohochud g Jiosh haꞌichu ahga ch ab t-wui gegok. Kumt am wo si e hoꞌigeꞌidahunad mat wo t-doꞌibia g Jiosh ab ha amjed.
\p 
\v 3 Jiosh at hemho wa am hab wo juh mo haschu i t-ahgid. S-mahch ach mat ab wo i em-mah g gewkdag k wo em-nuhkud mat pi wo em-gehg g Jiawul.
\v 4 Dam t-wehm wohochuddam. Kuch heg hekaj hab em-elid mam am hab junihim hegai mach ab i em-mashcham ch am hab wabsh wo i junihid.
\v 5 Ch ab i tahni g t-kownalig Jesus mat hab wo em-juh mamt baꞌich wo i mai g Jiosh pihk elidadag k wo s-chu nakogad hab masma mo hab masma g Jesus Christ.
\s1 Mattsh wo chum s-wapagimak
\p 
\v 6 Heki ach hu em-mashcham mamt wo s-wapagimak. K eda haꞌi hegam mo d wohochuddam s-papadma ch pi am hu oidch hab e junihim g t-mashchama. Ch ab em-chehani g t-kownalig Jesus Christ gewkdagkaj mamt pi am hu wo ha wehmajk.
\v 7 Am am wa t-neid mach wa pi shaꞌi papadma mach wa am em-wehmajkahim. Kum am wa s-mahch mamt am chum t-oidk hab wo wa masmak.
\v 8 Si ach wa chikpan chum hems s-chuhugam k ed matt am wo wa haꞌichu ha namkidad hegam mach hedai i kih am dadha mamt pi haꞌichu wo heki gei t-wehhejed.
\p 
\v 9 Bo hi wa chum mahs mach apꞌedag mamt ab haꞌichu wo i t-namkid nach pi d Jiosh pionag em-wehhejed. Ch wa wabshaba hejel t-dagioꞌid matt am wo em-chehgi mamt has wo chum masmak.
\v 10 Bach wa em-ahgid mach eda am em-wehmaj mamt pi wo ha gegos hegam mo pi tatchua mat wo chikpanad.
\v 11 Kah ach mo am em-shahgid haꞌi s-papadma ch pi chikpan ch wabsh himchud g has ahgadag.
\v 12 Ch ab si ha chehani g t-kownalig Jesus Christ gewkdagkaj ch ab ha gewkemhun mat am wabsh wo i e bahbgi k wo chikpanad ch hekaj wo e dagioꞌidad.
\p 
\v 13 Kumt ahpim mam wabsh s-ap am hab e junihim am hab wabsh wo i junihid g s-apꞌekam ch pi wo dagito
\v 14 ch wabshaba wabsh wo dagito hegai matp hedai pi ab hu wo wohog elidad ihda mani ia em-chehani. Tp hems ab wo wa bei g si edadag k am wo i e apꞌech.
\v 15 Am g wo s-chegitok mo pi d em-obga ch wabshaba d em-wepnag mamt ab wo shohbidad haꞌichukaj.
\s1 Mat ia i kuhgi g e-oꞌohana g Paul
\p 
\v 16 Chum at hekid am wo em-wehmajk g t-kownalig Jesus. Kuch ab tahni mat chum hekid baꞌich ab wo i em-mahkad g s-ap tahhadkam.
\p 
\v 17 Ahni Paul ant ia hahawa si hejel haꞌichu wo oꞌoha hab masma mani hab wa wua an wehs ni-oꞌohana ed. Mt hab masma wo s-mahchk mani d ahni.
\p 
\v 18 Neh, ab at wo baꞌich i s-em-hoꞌigeꞌel g t-kownalig Jesus Christ.
